Mesenchymal Stem Cells for Treating Alzheimer's Disease: Cell Therapy and 
Chemical Reagent Pretreatment.

Zhang K(1)(2), Du X(1)(2), Gao Y(1)(2), Liu S(1)(2), Xu Y(3)(4).

Author information:
(1)Department of Psychiatry, First Hospital/First Clinical Medical College of 
Shanxi Medical University, Taiyuan, China.
(2)Shanxi Key Laboratory of Artificial Intelligence Assisted Diagnosis and 
Treatment for Mental Disorder, First Hospital of Shanxi Medical University, 
Taiyuan, China.
