Angie-LAMP for diagnosis of human eosinophilic meningitis using dog as proxy: A 
LAMP assay for Angiostrongylus cantonensis DNA in cerebrospinal fluid.

Baláž V(1)(2), Rivory P(3), Hayward D(4), Jaensch S(4), Malik R(5), Lee R(6)(7), 
Modrý D(1)(8)(9), Šlapeta J(3)(10).

