Acceptance of genetic editing and of whole genome sequencing of human embryos by 
patients with infertility before and after the onset of the COVID-19 pandemic.

Neuhausser WM(1), Fouks Y(2), Lee SW(2), Macharia A(3), Hyun I(4), Adashi EY(5), 
