Lipid droplets and peroxisomes are co-regulated to drive lifespan extension in 
response to mono-unsaturated fatty acids.

Papsdorf K(1), Miklas JW(1), Hosseini A(1), Cabruja M(1), Morrow CS(2), Savini 
